Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&HF3912C&\blur1.5}昨天還並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:39.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\3c&HF3912C&\blur1.5}跟隨我腳步的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:44.71,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\3c&HF3912C&\blur1.5\bord1.5}看不到終點的迷宮 被雨淋濕的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:48.69,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\3c&HF3912C&\blur1.5\bord1.5}雖然沒有什麼後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:51.52,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,323)\3c&HF3A42D&\blur1.5}叫喊的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:56.50,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,323)\3c&HF3A42D&\blur1.5}一定會傳達到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.27,0:02:04.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&HBF9D8F&\blur1.5}在宣告這個故事開始的鐘聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:07.47,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,250)\3c&HBF9D8F&\blur1.5}所連接的旅途之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:12.51,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&HB64F38&\blur1.5}你所描繪的未來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:17.35,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H89B63F&\blur1.5}被指引到曾幾何時的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:22.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)\3c&H5187D8&\blur1.5}將兩份願望逐一化為有形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:27.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H5187D8&\blur1.5}將奇跡 不斷超越
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:32.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H44ACC3&\blur1.5}你所描繪的未來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:37.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H4697D0&\blur1.5}現在也在哪裏存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:44.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,450)\3c&HE4772B&\blur1.5}將那無論承載多少夢想 絕無虛偽的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:47.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,0)\3c&HB1601B&\blur1.5}Ah… Oh 一直做我自己
