Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2連拳 要攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「冰霧吐息」要來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3秒前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 我們上！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:51.89,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(640,543)}「誓約勝利之劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:51.89,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs38\pos(640,508)}Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻擊模式要改變了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了哥哥 光只剩下3片了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 那個skill什麼的招式不能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它還剩著2條血
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠我的「技能組合」沒法全打乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(578,670)}Skill Connection
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 防禦姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 buff被…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩乃！拜託你撐30秒！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼下去的話無法打倒「索列姆」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只剩下一個希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是被埋在這個房間某處的我一族的秘寶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 那個寶物是什麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:05:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概這個大小的 黃金之錘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錘…錘子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！用雷屬性的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷…雷擊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾雅 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涌出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涌現出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涌現…出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾雅…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這…這不是大叔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托爾…雷霆之神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無恥的巨人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢盜取吾等神器 雷霆之錘：「妙爾尼爾」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(913,670)}Mjolnir
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就讓你嘗嘗因果的報應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙的神啊 你竟敢欺騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我把你那滿臉的鬍子扯下來 然後送回「阿斯嘉特」去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁托爾吸引注意力的時候 大家一起攻擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 全力攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍技也盡量用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到地底去吧 巨人之王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就趁現在開心吧 小蟲子們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊 你們太相信「阿薩神族」的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你們 妖精的劍士們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我終於能一雪被奪去寶物的恥辱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得給你一點獎勵才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「雷錘妙爾尼爾」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(682,670)}Mjolnir
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在正義的戰鬥中好好使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你獲得了史詩級武器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…根本沒點戰錘類的技能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在…移動？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 在上浮？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…任務好像仍然在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精們啊 請進入「索列姆海姆」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將「誓約勝利之劍」從樞之座上拔下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(495,670)}Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你看 最後的光還在閃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 王座下面有階梯正在生成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系統命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物品ID 生成「誓約勝利之劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(752,670)}Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們見識一下你的毅力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「約頓海姆」要崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 快點脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 就讓你們看看本大爺奧林匹克垂直跳高術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克萊因 你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉法 還剩多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕上了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不完成任務的話 無法得到所有權嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽聽看 又有聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「頓其」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們轉移到「頓其」身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動作快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「頓其」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這對我而言 還是太沉重了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的「紅衣主教」這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(621,670)}Cardinal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概200米左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算再怎麼也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩…詩…詩…詩乃 你好帥啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會給你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別露出這張臉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這之前 和我做個約定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每當你用這把劍的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要想我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 受女孩子歡迎也很辛苦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我會想起然後向你道謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個迷宮 我們只不過探索了一次就崩壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點覺得可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 樹根上發芽了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「頓其」好像很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 「頓其」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 你有很多同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊有 那邊也有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這麼多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出色的完成了委託呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,削鐵如泥能斬斷一切樹木的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「誓約勝利之劍」已經移除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(559,670)}Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「約頓海姆」終於恢復了它本來的面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切都是各位的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的妹妹們也要向各位表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是貝爾丹迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們 妖精劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能再次看到生機盎然的「約頓海姆」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恍如夢境一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是史庫爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們 戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把那柄劍托付給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.79,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz3.614\c&H7B8082&\b1\frx354\fry0\pos(491,369)}任務報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.79,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H5E6467&\b0\frz3.998\frx354\fry4\pos(531,561)}「誓約勝利之劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.79,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H5E6467&\b0\fs25\frz3.998\frx354\fry4\pos(531,533)}Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精 謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就通關了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史庫爾德 能留個聯繫方式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克萊因 我現在是打心裏佩服你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到 而且很清楚 也聽得到 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是將DAISY CAFE的實時影像虛擬3D化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 現在試著慢慢移動看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在結衣應該能感覺到在這店裏飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說那個帶著麥克的監視器相當於結衣的終端感覺器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥在學校學 機…機械…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機械工程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選修了這個工程學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是為了課題做了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來都是為了結衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會不斷跟爸爸提出要求的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:52.76,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(523,520)\shad0\c&H18101D&\3c&H3A4B64&}本日包場!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:22:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝 得到聖劍「誓約勝利之劍」和「雷錘妙爾尼爾」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:22:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(563,670)}Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:22:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(976,670)}Mjolnir
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.37,0:22:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了 2025年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 為什麼是「誓約勝利之劍」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(791,670)}Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科幻小說和漫畫一般都是用「湖中劍」的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(868,670)}Calibur
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是「誓約勝利之劍」…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(661,670)}Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你問這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 詩乃 你讀這類書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為中學的時候我喜歡泡在圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞瑟王的書也讀過幾本
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺都是「湖中劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(723,670)}Calibur
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確 最原始的傳說都有各式各樣的叫法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.53,0:22:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼寫也許不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槍的口徑 英語也讀作Caliber
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衍生含義還代表人的器量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那我得記下來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考試應該不會考這些的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說「誓約勝利之劍」的所有者應該有相應的器量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(434,670)}Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說最近某人通過短期打工狠狠的賺了一筆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.85,0:23:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當…當然 我早就決定好今天這頓算我賬上的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(368,710)}謝謝…桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(897,710)}謝謝…前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(131,710)}謝謝…哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集 森林之家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
